<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Welcome to Register</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/signup.css" />
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div id="notice" class="mb-2">
      테스트 웹 회원가입 페이지입니다.
    </div>
    <form id="formSignUp" method="post">
      <div id="signupText">회원가입</div>
      <div class="input-group mt-2">
        <label class="form-label" for="id">ID</label>
        <input id="id" type="text" class="form-control" name="signupID" placeholder="I  D" required>
      </div>
      <div class="input-group mt-2 mb-2">
        <span class="form-text">특수문자 + 영문 + 숫자의 조합으로 12자 이상으로 구성</span>
        <input id="pw" class="form-control" type="password" name="signupPW" placeholder="P  W" required>
        <input id="confirm_pw" class="form-control" type="password" name="signupPW_confirm" placeholder="CONFIRM" required>
      </div>
      <div class="input-group mb-2">
        <button id="btnSubmit" class="btn btn-outline-success" type="submit" name="btnSubmit">회원가입</button>
      </div>
    </form>
